{
  "stem": "9995.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But my mother said, don't go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because when I come in, they always ask if somebody knows typing, steno, this and that, but you don't have those skills.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Therefore, you-- you are in danger, and I am not.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she went to Auschwitz, and that's exactly what happened.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They asked, who can do this and that?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They try her, and instead of going to Auschwitz Birkenau, which was the-- she went to Auschwitz [INAUDIBLE], and she had more food and was working in an office.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I stayed over there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I got job in [INAUDIBLE] which was they were making nice clothes for the top Germans.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "However, I was very bright, and the woman who was in charge of it, her name was Mrs.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Goodman, didn't like that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So she took me, and I had to start fire in the offices of all the Germans over there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was 11 offices.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And each one of them was giving me either piece of paper or something and said, start fire with this.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And if I didn't, they were hitting you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But after a while, they were not-- they weren't hitting me too much.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So, but somehow, I became such an expert in lighting this with just minimal amount of things which you need to start fire, that it was OK.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And however, one day, one German who, like my husband, he was a big killer, he wanted to punish him.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So he called me, and he asked him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He never called my husband Hilfstein, but Hilfswine, which means like swine is a pig.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he said that he should call me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when I came in, he ask him, is this [GERMAN] frau?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He said, jawohl Herr [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He said, [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
